description:
7000 bornes, une frontiere

Travel Documentary hosted by Alex Mayenfisch, published by TV5Monde in 2012 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/4/4b/7000-bornes-une-frontiere-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
7000 border markers, a frontier.

Switzerland's borders stretch across thousands of kilometres. An in-between world delineating a zone, historically and now, the border separates but also unites. We often cross it, but rarely hang around too long.
